## Disclaimer

This software is provided for educational and demonstration purposes. While it includes realistic business logic and data structures, it uses mock data and should not be used for actual customer service operations without proper data integration and security measures.

The voice agent system is designed to showcase AI-powered customer service capabilities and should be thoroughly tested and validated before any production deployment.

---

## Data Privacy Notice

This software may process voice data and customer information. Users are responsible for:
- Obtaining proper consent for voice recording and processing
- Complying with applicable data protection regulations (GDPR, CCPA, etc.)
- Implementing appropriate security measures for sensitive data
- Ensuring proper data retention and deletion policies

IndiVillage Tech Solutions is committed to data privacy and security in all its solutions.